---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Card from "../components/Card.astro";
import Logo from "../assets/orbwalkerfinal.png";
---

<Layout title="Orbwalker">
	<main class='centerContents'>
		<div class="logoContainer centerContents">
			<img class='logo' src={Logo} alt="orbwalker logo">
			<h1 class='headTitle'>Grassroots esports and media solutions</h1>
		</div>
		<div class="videoContainer centerContents">
			<iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/2DcDTVFmj5Y" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0"
				allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
				allowfullscreen />
		</div>

		<div class="cards centerContents">
			<Card href='#' title='Remote'>For cost, safety, or convenience, we can get your event online for viewing
				across
				the globe.</Card>
			<Card href='#' title='In Person'>Whether you have a theatre, a LAN center, a bar, or a stadium, we'll find a
				solution for your venue.</Card>
			<Card href='#' title='Mixed'>Not quite remote, not quite in person? No problem. We'll connect staff and
				transition seamlessly.</Card>
			<Card href='#' title='Affordable'>We believe in fair, transparent pricing. We'll only advocate for what you
				need
				and won't surprise you with expensive features you don't want.</Card>
			<Card href='#' title='Flexible'>We're experienced integrating different teams and equipment including
				facility
				staff or volunteers looking for valuable experience.</Card>
			<Card href='#' title='Fun'>Events are entertainment first and foremost, and we never forget that.</Card>
		</div>


	</main>
</Layout>

<style lang='scss'>
	main {
		flex-direction: column;
	}


	.logoContainer {
		flex-direction: column;

		h1.headTitle {
			text-align: center;
			font-weight: 400;
			font-size: min(4vw, 2rem);
			text-transform: uppercase;
		}

		.logo {
			width: 80%;
			max-height: 8rem;
		}
	}

	.videoContainer {
		width: 80%;

		iframe {
			// width: 100%;
			// height: min(30vw, 25rem);
			min-height: 30vw;
			max-height: 30rem;
			aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
			margin-inline: 0;
		}

		margin-block: 2.5rem;

	}


	.cards {

		flex-direction: row;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		flex-basis: 10rem;
		flex-shrink: 1;
	}
</style>